snippet.title: The funniest and most entertaining ANIMAL videos #5 - Funny animal compilation - Watch & laugh!
snippet.description:
Animals make us laugh and happy, who doesn't like animals?! Just look at all these cats, kittens, puppies, dogs, raccoons, squirrels, penguins, goats,.. and how they behave, make funny sounds, sleep and snore, play, fail,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
